Schedule, ver 1.0 - software requirements specification

All specificity of the program will be listed below:

Written in HTML, CSS, JavaScript, Python and SQL.
Uses Flask as its framework, and Jinja as template engine.
Allow user to:
	create new account;
	modify their email and/or password;
	add notes, modify or exclude them;
	schedule tasks on calendar, change their date or exclude them;
	list goals, and exclude them if desired;
	have a break at coffee time, with possibly some games;
	customize the page by changing its color (dark/white mode);
	add or remove files in a simple file manager;
	login and logout.
